"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-news-ap-spain-paris-kevin-durant-olympians-b2586962.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  TheOlympianswere wet for hours.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For some, it did not matter.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others had to navigate the unexpected conditions and make the most of it.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from around the world paraded on boats in rain-soaked uniforms for Friday's soggy opening ceremony of theParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The four-hour event on the Seine River went on despite rain throughout the evening, ranging from light showers to intense downpours.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It made for less than ideal conditions for athletes preparing to begin intense competition across Paris.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.685449225661149e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few events, including soccer and rugby sevens, began days before the opening ceremony, but much of the action got underway Saturday.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding, originally set to open Saturday, was postponed because of the rain.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Technically, standing in the rain and cold alone is not what makes people sick.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being in those conditions for long periods of time can affect the immune system, though.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is why Austrian marathon swimmer Jan Hercog said Friday he was taking vitamin C and other supplements to get through the ceremony.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9800848346033858, \"rank\": 0.01857620653630853, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from some countries had no concerns at all.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They grabbed umbrellas and ponchos, and their show went on.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I waited until a little bit into the rain (before putting on the poncho), so I was pretty wet when I put it on, but that's OK,\\\"Spainwomen's basketball player Megan Gustafson said.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Gustafson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megan Gustafson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Gustafson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Gustafson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was still fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of practice Saturday in Villneuve-d'Ascq, where the Olympics are playing the group stage for basketball, Gustafson said the rain was not an issue during the ceremony even if the ponchos messed with staying fashionable.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gustafson, 27, also wasn't worried about catching a cold on the verge of her Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain, which finished sixth in Tokyo after winning silver at the 2016 Rio Games, opens group play for the women Sunday against China at Pierre Mauroy Stadium.\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.974057784546982, \"rank\": 0.025621570519468086, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 2046, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7981540729309641, \"rank\": 0.2528661749225517, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.7839565196614271, \"rank\": 0.268890930681546, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The weather was relatively warm and the rain wasn't super cold or anything, so I felt comfortable,\\\" Gustafson said.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think any of my teammates are sick, so we are all right.\\\"\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States women's basketball team left the ceremony early and got on their buses from Paris back to Lille.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9737095284762116, \"rank\": 0.026857429040405122, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2455, \"end\": 2460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.685449225661149e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2469, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.9999452291142417, \"rank\": 5.477388556419646e-05, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was raining.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if you guys saw,\\\" WNBA star A'ja Wilson deadpanned.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"A'ja Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A little weather issue.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't really into everything as much as I wanted to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maksym Cheberiaka, spokesperson for Ukraine's Olympic Committee, said that Ukrainian athletes did not have any health concerns because of the rain.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.7344669304804379, \"rank\": 0.36126177037730905, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.6886649015146603, \"rank\": 0.4514743516586181, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who had competitions scheduled for Saturday either did not participate or left the ceremony early.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. flag bearers LeBron James and Coco Gauff wore the clear plastic ponchos to protect their matching white jackets.\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2900, \"end\": 2909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.325374839719374e-19, \"text\": \"U.S. flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2918, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were smiling and laughing, but they were drenched.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A phenomenal experience, obviously, to be there with my fellow Olympians,\\\" James said.\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.88565632803133, \"rank\": 0.0936390189817336, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was representing the red, white and blue, I was representing our country.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very humbling and an honor to be part of that group, all the athletes from all the different states and cities all around America.\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And just being on one boat and representing us for the start of the games, it was a true honor.\\\"\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow basketball OlympianKevin Durant, who could join James in the team's Olympic opener Sunday, posted a photo of himself in the U.S. outfit for the opening - navy blazer, button-down shirt, denim jeans - on Instagram with the caption \\\"Whole outfit soaked but we here.\\\"\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 0.9980277294727281, \"rank\": 0.00197437654155624, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 3529, \"end\": 3534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.88565632803133, \"rank\": 0.0936390189817336, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 3684, \"end\": 3693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.040326865568847e-29, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were soaking,\\\" James said.\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3766, \"end\": 3771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.88565632803133, \"rank\": 0.0936390189817336, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you saw KD's post, he was not telling any fibs.\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3790, \"end\": 3792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khaki_drill\", \"score\": 0.999994880177756, \"rank\": 5.055858816832479e-06, \"text\": \"KD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khaki_drill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khaki_drill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were pretty drenched when we got back to the hotel.\\\"\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. men's coach Steve Kerr wasn't at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3887, \"end\": 3891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996002304588049, \"rank\": 0.0003458651660966771, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3904, \"end\": 3914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That means he stayed dry.\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was watching on TV seeing all the rain,\\\" Kerr said.\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is not ideal, but I think it'll be an experience and a memory that these guys will have for life that will far exceed the inconvenience of the rain.\\\"\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  Associated Press writer Hannah Arhirova andAPSports Writers Doug Feinberg, Tim Reynolds, Teresa Walker contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4191, \"end\": 4207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999914152795, \"rank\": 8.584912350396911e-09, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Reynolds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tim Reynolds\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Reynolds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Reynolds\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP Olympics: https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4328, \"end\": 4330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.488803100778039e-14, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}]}"